About Clean-Aire

Trusted and Reliable Service

Our aircon services are designed to provide you with exceptional comfort and peace of mind. We understand the importance of a well-functioning air conditioning system, especially during hot summer months or in tropical climates.

Professional Service

Our skilled technicians are dedicated to ensuring that your aircon operates at its optimal level, delivering cool and refreshing air throughout your space. Whether you need routine maintenance, repairs, or installation of a new unit, we have the expertise to meet your needs.

Range of expertise

Our comprehensive range of services includes thorough inspections, cleaning of filters and coils, refrigerant level checks, condenser and evaporator coil cleaning, fan motor lubrication, and overall system diagnostics. We strive to enhance the efficiency and longevity of your air conditioning system, saving you energy and preventing potential breakdowns.
